codeText: @Override_    public void populateExchange(Exchange exchange) {_        StringBuffer fileExtracted = new StringBuffer()__        List<DbxEntry> entries = null__        if (resultEntries != null) {_            entries = (List<DbxEntry>) resultEntries__            for (DbxEntry entry : entries) {_                fileExtracted.append(entry.name + "-" + entry.path + "\n")__            }_        }_        exchange.getIn().setHeader(DropboxResultHeader.FOUNDED_FILES.name(), fileExtracted.toString())__        exchange.getIn().setBody(entries)__    }
